snippet.title: PLANTS vs ZOMBIES: The Last Stand JACKPOT! - Arcade Ticket Game
snippet.description:
We found the arcade version of Plants VS Zombies!! If you have not played the popular game Plants vs Zombies, the goal is to eliminate all the zombies before they get to your base. In the case of the arcade version, the base is your lone peashooter(firing plant). If the zombies make it to your peashooter they will eat your brains and you lose!

Let's see how good we can do.
